title: Tube (discrete curves)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

For a discrete ribbon $$(\gamma,N),$$ the discrete tube around it is given by
$$
(i,j) \mapsto
  \tfrac12 (\gamma_i + \gamma_{i+1}) +
  \varepsilon e^{2\pi\i\frac jm} N_i
$$
for some small enough $$\varepsilon > 0.$$